column2: Christians in your Realm will be gravely insulted.
Infidels in your realm are insulted.
[jeanne_darc.GetFirstName] the Maid of [home_of_jeanne_darc.GetName] has arrived at the court of [Root.GetTitledName].
Many members of the realm's clergy will be angry with [Root.GetTitledFirstName].
Many of the lords in the realm will be angry with [Root.GetTitledFirstName].
It had better not rain any more.
The preparations for this year's Passover festival begin.\n
You send out invitations to your Jewish vassals for the traditional Passover Seder dinner.
Construction on the Third Temple has begun.
